('104614', 'ROTARY MICROTOME', 'Dental', 'Oral Pathology', 'Microtomes', 7.1, '<p>\r\nROTARY MICROTOME is designed to enhance manual sectioning. It\r\nis based on taper roller guides with high precision screw which provides accuracy and stability\r\nfor sectioning. This Microtome has been designed for effortless manual sectioning using\r\ncounter balanced handwheel. The blade holder is suitable for high & low profile blade. The\r\nspacious section waste tray collects sectioning waste during trimming and sectioning. <br /><br />\r\n<b>Technical Specifications: </b>\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Section thickness setting range : 0.5-60pm \r\n<li>Setting Values : 0.5-2pm increment step 0.5pm,  2-20um increment step 1pm, 20-60pm increment step 5pm\r\n<li>Minimum Setting Value : 0.5 pm\r\n<li>Trimming thickness setting range : 1-60 pm\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\nComplete as above and supplied with sample pack of disposable blades.\r\n</p>', 'images/products/Dental/Oral-Pathology/104614.png', '', '2014-07-18 13:23:18'),
