('320770', 'MOISTURE BALANCE', 'Dental', 'Oral Pathology', 'Equipments', 7.4, '<p>\r\nInfra Red Moisture Balance: The balance is calibrated in terms of\r\nmoisture percentage 0-100% and is read directly on the instrument.\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Measuring Range: 0 to 100%,\r\n<li>Lamp : 250W Infrared Lamp\r\n<li>Readability :0.2% \r\n<li>Accuracy : + 0.2%\r\n<li>Mains : 230voIts, 50Hz\r\n<li>Capacity : 5 or 10 or 20 or 25 gms\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n<i>(Any one capacity- please specify your requirement)</i>\r\nSupplied with bend thermometer; 12 Nos Aluminium disposal pan, pair forceps & Instruction\r\nManual. \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nInfra Red Moisture Balance (Auto Transformer) Same as Model\r\nMMB-11 but supplied with auto transformer\r\n</p>', 'images/products/Dental/Oral-Pathology/320770.png', '', '2014-07-18 13:59:52'),
