('340545', 'BITE WING FILM HOLDER', 'Dental', 'Oral Medicine and Radiology', 'Positioning-Devices', 1.5, '<p>Universal film holder. Great for bite-wing x-rays!  </p>\r\n<ol><li>Long cone paralleling technique  </li>\r\n<li>Target points for accurate alignment   </li> \r\n<li>Sliding film carrier has three click-stop positions  </li>\r\n<li>Handles #0, #1, #2 film horizontally or vertically  </li>\r\n<li> For steam autoclave </li>\r\n</ol>', 'images/products/Dental/Oral-Medicine-and-Radiology/340545.png', '', '2014-07-17 13:23:00'),
('340637', 'DIGITAL PULP TESTER', 'Dental', 'Oral Medicine and Radiology', 'Equipments', 1.2, '<p>The Gentle-Pulse vitality tester is a hand-held device that identifies a vital tooth by stimulating it with a weak current. Vital teeth should sense the mild stimulus long before it causes discomfort. As the operator turns a knob, the strength of the stimulus increases: <ol><li>Stimulates a response from vital teeth without approaching the pain threshold.</li> \r\n<li>Unique integrated circuitry generates a complex pulsed waveform that the patient senses before it becomes painful. </li>\r\n<li>Features a large numeric readout.</li>\r\n<li>Three rates of stimulus increase - slow, medium and fast.</li>\r\n<li>Delivers gradual stimulus increases - no sudden jumps to trigger pain.</li>\r\n<li>Easy push-button activation.</li>\r\n<li>Runs on easily replaceable 9-V battery.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</p>', 'images/products/Dental/Oral-Medicine-and-Radiology/340637.png', '', '2014-07-17 12:59:25'),
