('411437', 'NEW SLIDE STAINING MACHINE ', 'Dental', 'Oral Pathology', 'Equipments', 7.4, '<p>\r\n SLIDE STAINING MACHINE WITH TOUCH SCREEN: \r\nLinear Slide Stainer is an enclosed compact bench top unit. It has a user friendly software.\r\nThe lowering and lifting of a tissue basket is smooth and noiseless. Features touch screen    \r\nLCD with user friendly software. All the reagents are covered when not in use to minimize \r\nloss due to evaporation. Illumination of the working chamber enables clear view of the \r\nprocess. The whole equipment is enclosed and an exhaust fan is provided to dispose off\r\nreagent vapors away from the laboratory.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<b>Technical Specification: </b>\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>No. of Cylinder : 14 \r\n<li>Cylinder Capacity : 1000mI \r\n<li>Slide Processing Staining : 72 Slides \r\n<li>Programmable : Yes\r\n</ol>', 'images/products/Dental/Oral-Pathology/411437.png', '', '2014-07-18 13:58:17'),
