('466766', 'OVARIAN SHIELD & GONAD SHIELD', 'Medical', 'X-Ray Apron', '', 0, '<p><b> Ovarian & Gonad Shield</b> ensures that the male genital region and female ovarian region is adequately shielded against the X-Ray penetration.</p>\r\n<p>Care has been taken to avoid irritation in men wearing Gonad shield & women wearing Ovarian shield</p>', 'images/products/Medical/X-Ray-Apron/466766.png', '', '2013-12-02 08:25:23'),
