('481323', 'POLARIMETER', 'Dental', 'Oral Pathology', 'Equipments', 7.4, '<p>\r\nLAURENT''S HALF SHADE POLARIMETER: Vernier reading 1/10.\r\nSupplied with 200mm Polarimeter tube, a hand magnifier for vernier reading, in a storing\r\ncabinet.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nRESEARCH POLARIMETER(220 MM) accept observation tubes upto \r\n220mm length. The angular scale from 0 to 360° is sub divided to 1° to enable direct reading \r\nto 0.5° and by estimation 0.02°. The sugar scale ranges of 30° to 120° I.S.S. Units enables\r\ndirects reading to 0.1 with estimation of 0.5 sugar degree. Supplied complete with polarimeter \r\ntubes 200mm instruction manual and dust cover and standard accessories in the box.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n Sodium lamp with Power Supply for the above \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nREASERCH POLARIMETER (220mm) TRIPLE FIELD: Same as MP-01\r\nbut supplied with all imported optical components with triple half shadow effects.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nRESEARCH POLARIMETER (400mm): Equipped with latest imported \r\noptical system, its highly accurate glass scale is divided to read angular degrees and also \r\ncarries sugar scale in I.S.S. Units. The angular scale from 0 to 360° is sub divided to 1 degree \r\nto enable direct reading to 0.5° and by estimation 0.02°. The sugar scale range from 30° to \r\n120° I.S.S. units enables direct reading to 0.1 and by estimating of 0.5 sugar degree. Supplied  it\r\nwith all standard accessories. \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nSodium lamp with power Supply for Above.\r\n</p> \r\n<p>\r\nRESEARCH POLARIMETER( 400mm) TRIPLE FIELD: Same as MP-\r\n02 but supplied with all imported components and triple half shadow effect.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<b>ACCESSORIES FOR POLARIMETER</b>\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>POLARIMETER TUBE(SIDE FILLING) 100m Polarimeter Tube -\r\nMade of Corning glass with screw caps and bubble trap length of 50mm, 94.5mm, 100mm\r\n<li>Polarimeter Tube 200/220 mm Same as above but with\r\n200/220 mm length.\r\n<li>Polarimeter Tube 400 mm Same as above but 400mm length\r\n<li>Polarimeter Tube Cover Glass with rubber washer\r\n(Optically true) Per Dozen.\r\n<li>Polarimeter Tube(centre FiIIing)100mm\r\n<li>Polarimeter Tube200mm\r\n<li>Polarimeter Tube 400mm\r\n</ol>\r\n', 'images/products/Dental/Oral-Pathology/481323.png', '', '2014-07-18 14:00:22'),
('481445', 'PHYSIO DISPENSER', 'Dental', 'Prosthodontics', 'Equipments', 6.1, '<p>Mariotti introduces the MiniUniko economical version. Always with high performance, it combines ease of use and practicality. Miniuniko.F can be set in a few seconds thanks to an innovative software and a great flexibility which allow to use and adapt the various implantology systems. <br /><br /><b>SPECIFICATIONS</b></p>\r\n<ol><li>Power supply: 230/125 Vac - 50/60Hz\r\n<li>Absorbed power: 109 VA \r\n<li>Maximum Torque: limited a 60Ncm \r\n<li>Insulation: Class 1, type BF \r\n<li>Motor speed: 200-30000 rpm\r\n<li>Peristaltic pump max irrigation: 90 ml/min\r\n<li>Control box dimension: mm 245x245x100\r\n<li>Pedal: motor or motor+pump on/off\r\n<li>Main functions: control of speed, torque, peristaltic pump, handpiece \r\nreduction, reverse, 4 programs, software upgraded, autoclavable motor/cable/connector.</ol>\r\n<p><b>ACCESSORIES</b><br /><br /> \r\nArt. C20 Implantology contra-angle for finest quality. Micro-head, 20:1 reduction, \r\nexternal sprayer with possible internal spraying.</p>', 'images/products/Dental/Prosthodontics/481445.png', '', '2014-07-18 07:32:05'),
