('576751', 'PICKLING KIT', 'Dental', 'Endodontics', 'Equipments', 4.1, '<p>An electrically operated container which thermostatically heats liquid (diluted sulphuric acid or safety pickle) in which jewellery or small articles are cleaned after being heated/soldered.</p>\r\n<ol><li>Made with an acid proof casing, the internal beaker and lid are made of plastic\r\n<li>Tools like steel  tweezers are no longer needed.\r\n<li>The modern and practical unit to rationally acidify precious metal work-pieces. The work-piece are placed into the swing-sieve on the cover and then immersed into the bath.\r\n<li>Electrically heated with thermostatic control\r\n<li>Integrated swing-sieve made of acid-resistant polypropylene on the lid\r\n<li>Chassis made of acid-resistant and impact resistant polypropylene\r\n<li>Low power consumption</ol>\r\n<p><b>Technical data</b></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Power supply : 230/240 V\r\n<li>Power frequency : 50/60 Hz\r\n<li>Power consumption : 40/60 W\r\n<li>Size ( H x W x D ) : 190 x 170 x 180 mm\r\n<li>Weight : 1 kg\r\n</ol>\r\n', 'images/products/Dental/Endodontics/576751.png', '', '2014-07-18 07:53:17'),
