ose Heating can\r\nbe controlled through microprocessor and it can be programmed for the weekdays.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nSame as above but with 5L capacity of the paraffin tank.\r\n</p>', 'images/products/Dental/Oral-Pathology/588867.png', '', '2014-07-18 13:42:06'),
('589050', 'MANUAL CRYOSTAT MICROTOME', 'Dental', 'Oral Pathology', 'Microtomes', 7.1, '<p>\r\n\r\nCRYOCUT: The cooling system incorporates P.I.D Temperature\r\nController and a sealed compressor to ensure quick cooling up to -30°C and trouble free\r\nperformance. Automatic Specimen Retracting Device prevents damage to the specimen on the    \r\nreturn upward stroke and assures uniform perfect sectioning. A circular slide system is \r\nprovided for easy removal of section with minimal disturbance of iso thermal conditions. Large \r\nstainless steel chamber permits adequate storage facilities for housing of retracting microtome \r\nand accessories. With feed range from 0 to 20 microns in step of 1 micron each. It \r\nincorporates retracting mechanism for best result in sectioning a wide variety of tissues.<br /><br />\r\n<b>Technical Specifications:  </b>\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Section thickness : 1-20pm in 1pm steps\r\n<li>Section size :40x50mm\r\n<li>Temperature range : up to -30° C accuracy +/- 2° C\r\n<li>Chamber size : Z2" x 15" x 10"\r\n<li>Cabinet size : 25" x 28" x 50"\r\n<li>Instrument port : 4" diameter\r\n<li>Window opening : 14.5" x 9"\r\n<li>Refrigeration : Hermetically sealed and thermostatically controlled \r\n<li>Weight : Approx. 85 Kg\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\nSupplied complete with a razor 120mm long with back handle, honing stone,\r\noil can, wooden Cabinet, freezing attachment & dust cover\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nCRYOCUT SENIOR is suitable for lower temperature range up to\r\n-40°C with electronic temperature control and digital display.\r\n</p>', 'images/products/Dental/Oral-Pathology/589050.png', '', '2014-07-18 13:26:53'),
('589202', 'PACQUETTE BLADE HOLDER', 'Dental', 'Periodontics', 'Speciality-Instruments', 2.2, '<p>For Palatal Surgery and other bowed blade techniques.Improved blade holding mechanism for use with bowed blade concept pioneered by Uohara-Federbusch.One half of a double edged razor blade is placed between faces of the wedge and inner surfaces of wedge recess and securely locked in place as wedge is drawn tight.</p>', 'images/products/Dental/Periodontics/589202.png', '', '2014-07-18 07:06:29'),
('59020', 'X-RAY READER (USB)', 'Dental', 'Oral Medicine and Radiology', 'Scanners-and-Camera', 1.3, '<ol><li>It can make common X-ray become digital X-ray immediately,  \r\nand save them into computer \r\n<li>It can zoom the X-ray about 50 times on the monitor, dentist can communicate \r\nwith their patients more conveniently \r\n<li>Dentists don''t need to setup driver, it can be used in any time</ol> \r\n <p><b>Specification:</b></p> \r\n<ol><li>Voltage:  DC 5V ( support by computer) \r\n<li>Power: 300 mA \r\n<li>Signal output: USB 2.0 \r\n<li>Volume: 70mm*84mm*80mm \r\n<li>Weight: 430g \r\n<li>Accessories: X-ray salver,image software, USB connect cable </ol>', 'images/products/Dental/Oral-Medicine-and-Radiology/59020.png', '', '2014-07-17 13:07:15'),
('594024', 'GP TRIMMER', 'Dental', 'Endodontics', 'Equipments', 4.1, '<p>\r\n<b>Usage: </b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nG/P TRIMMER is a dental treatment device cutting the end of the gutta percha points with in a moment by one\r\ntouching a button.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<b>Features:</b>\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li> G/P Trimmer has eliminated completely the possibility of burns that might be caused by traditional method\r\nusing this renovated equipment.\r\n<li>One touching a button, intended treatment will be completed with in a moment without any fear of pain or\r\ndiscomfort for the user.\r\n<li>The best of merit is fast. The Cutting Tip is heated in 2~3 seconds, enable to cut the gutta percha points.\r\nFurther, the Cutting Tip cools down fast.\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n<b>Product information:</b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nG/P(Gutta Percha) Trimmer is a cutting device that can help the dentistry medical treatment. It is the most convenient\r\nand easy to use after filling up with Gutta Percha Point. It is based on R & D.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<b>Components</b>\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>G.P Trimmer Hand piece : 1\r\n<li> hand piece holder : 1\r\n<li>Heat Cutting Tip : 4\r\n<li>Rechargeable Battery (1.2V Ni-MH) : 2\r\n<li>Battery Charger(option) : 1\r\n<li>Heat Cutting Tip Specification\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n<b>Functions and Product features:</b>\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>No more primitive flame\r\n<li>Accurate and precise cutting using various type of head\r\n<li>Easy and fast operation\r\n<li>Sanitary\r\n<li>No need assistant\r\n<li>Lightweight\r\n<li>Rechargeable battery operation\r\n<li>Fashionable and practical product design\r\n<li>CE certified and FDA registered\r\n<li>Tested and approved in accordance with internationally recognized standards as medical device\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n<b>Before use:</b>\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Do not charge the battery more than 12 hours. It is in the process of charging when the light is on.\r\n<li>Discharge the battery completely at least three times before recharging. It helps to have maximum result.\r\n<li>Can be used more then 100 times per charge.\r\n<li>If extra Cutting Tip is needed, please contact where it''s been purchased.\r\n<li>Please try using a Rechargeable Ni-MH battery with AA size 1.2V, 2300mA when battery has gone or been\r\nlost.\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n<b>How to use:</b>\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Put the Heat Cutting Tip into Hand Piece tightly. Press the ON-switch and check the temperature that is\r\nascended. Then turn off the switch until you use.\r\n<li>Access the Heat Cutting Tip to a cavity of the patient.\r\n<li>Press the ON-switch from the Canal to operate.\r\n<li>Cutting Tip is heated in 2~3 seconds, enabled to cut the Gutta Percha Points.\r\n<li>It operates while you hold the switch pressed.\r\n<li>Please take out from the mouth carefully even though the Cutting Tip cools down fast.\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n<b>Control and Maintain:</b>\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Clean up the remained Gutta Percha from the Cutting Tip using the Cotton pellet.\r\n<li>Wipe the Cutting Tip with an antiseptic solution.\r\n<li>You can autoclave sterilization the Tip.\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n<b>Attention/Caution:</b>\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>It is possible to bend the Cutting Tip slightly with gentle touch.\r\n<li>Do not bend the Cutting Tip when it is connected with Head Piece.\r\n<li>While using G/P Trimmer, do not touch the Cutting Tip by hand. You could burn yourself.\r\n<li>If there is no vibration by G/P Trimmer, change the battery.\r\n<li>If you operated continually more than 20 seconds, you must be rest at least for 10 seconds.\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'images/products/Dental/Endodontics/594024.png', '', '2014-07-18 07:51:37'),
