('643463', 'FULLY AUTOMATIC CRYOSTAT MICROTOME', 'Dental', 'Oral Pathology', 'Microtomes', 7.1, '<p>\r\nFULLY AUTOMATIC CRYOSTAT MICROTOME: The cryostat is\r\nergonomically designed keeping in view user needs and safety. It incorporates an optimized \r\ncooling system (double compressor) with rapid specimen freezing and smooth precise \r\norientation for high quality sectioning in histology, pro-environment refrigerant, a rapid \r\nrefrigeration mode, a peltier unit, and a LCD Screen which displays data such as sample \r\ntravel, section thickness and temperature. A Motorized handwheel movement is provided in \r\nthree speed mode: low, medium and high depending upon the tissue. It can be easily \r\nprogrammed for both start and stop. Easy to operate control panel with controls for \r\ntemperature and time. UV Sterilization is used for disinfection. Equipped with a closed \r\ndrainage system that ensures collection of condensed and defrost fluids in a container.<br /><br />\r\n<b>Salient Features: </b>\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Powerful sectioning motor\r\n<li>Specimen retraction function protects the specimen from blade injury\r\n<li>Trimming/Sectioning button makes it easy to switch to the desired mode\r\n<li>Rapid Refrigeration Mode allows desired temperature drop in 60mins MCM\r\n<li>Microprocessor based digital P.I.D temperature control\r\n<li>Power saving refrigeration system\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n<b>Technical Specifications:</b>\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Section Thickness Range : 1pm-60um\r\n<li>1pm-10pm, in 1pm increment \r\n<li>10pm-20pm, in 2pm increments \r\n<li>20pm-60um, in 5pm increments\r\n<li>Trimming Range : 10pm-300um in 10pm increments\r\n<li>Specimen Retraction : 5-75pm in 5pm increments\r\n<li>Lowest Temp. of Peltier Unit : -50°c\r\n<li>Cooling Downtime to -30°c : 60 mins\r\n<li>Maximum Specimen Size : 35mm x 35mm\r\n<li>Specimen Vertical Stroke : 65mm\r\n<li>Specimen Horizontal Feed : 25mm\r\n</ol>', 'images/products/Dental/Oral-Pathology/643463.png', '', '2014-07-18 13:26:26'),
('644897', 'MINI APRON', 'Medical', 'X-Ray Apron', '', 0, '<p>When you require protection only below the abdomen, <b> Mini Apron</b> scores a notch above others.</p>\r\n<p>Stylish, elegant and stylish are the attributes of the Mini Apron that make it a preferred choice of radiologists.</p>', 'images/products/Medical/X-Ray-Apron/644897.png', '', '2013-12-02 08:25:50'),
('645904', 'TENS MULTI CHANNEL', 'Dental', 'Oral Medicine and Radiology', 'Equipments', 1.2, '<p>\r\nDIGITENS 104 is an advanced micro controller based Four Channel TENS from HMS R & D. Unique design with manual\r\nand 20 pre-programs. Used for both fitness and therapeutic purpose. Soft touch keys for selection of programs. Built in\r\nbattery with 10 hrs backup indigenous design with international standards.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<b>SPECIFICATIONS</b>\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Tens Frequency - 2 – 250Hz (1 Hz Step)\r\n<li>Pulse width - 20 – 250 micro seconds\r\n<li>No.of Channels - Four\r\n<li>Output mode - Continuous/Pulsed\r\n<li>Frequency Sweep - Available\r\n<li>Treatment Time - 0 – 60 min\r\n<li>Pre-program - 1-15 Pain Relieving Program\r\n<li>16-20 Fitness Program\r\n<li>Display - 128 / 64 Graphic LCD Display\r\n<li>Power Source - Dual Power (Mains/Battery)\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n<b>FEATURES</b>\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>4 Channel Outputs\r\n<li>Micro controller based circuitry\r\n<li>Manual Cum preprograms facility\r\n<li>Obesity Program\r\n<li>Universal Input\r\n<li>Built In Re-chargeable battery with 10 hrs Back-up\r\n<li>ABS Cabinet-Portable & Light Weight\r\n<li>Mains Input Voltage - 90 V – 270V AC\r\n<li>Battery - Maintenance free rechargeable\r\n<li>Safety Class -\r\n<li>Dimensions - L x B x H – 21 x 22.5 x 6.5 cms\r\n<li>Weight - 1.75 Kgs\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n<b>TECHNICAL DATA</b>\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Class I, Type BF (IEC 60601 -1)\r\n<li>DIGITENS 104\r\n<li>DIGITENS 104\r\n<li>HMS\r\n</ol>\r\n', 'images/products/Dental/Oral-Medicine-and-Radiology/645904.png', '', '2014-07-17 13:03:42'),
