('861999', 'TISSUE FLOTATION BATH RECTANGULAR SHAPE', 'Dental', 'Oral Pathology', 'Equipments', 7.4, '<p>\r\nIdeally suited for preparing distortion less and wrinkle free tissue specimen. Its racktangular ,\r\ndouble walled, single piece inner and outer chamber are made of M/S, inside aluminum anodized\r\nblack and outer surface finished in parrot white stoved enamel, with wide enough rim for drying\r\nthe wet slides. Temperature is controlled by EGO/JUMO. German make capillary type thermostat,\r\nform ambient to 70°C with an accuracy of 2°C. supplied complete with pilot light, cord and.\r\nSuitable to work on 220V, single phase, 50Hz, AC supply\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Chamber Size: Dia Depth Rim Thermostatically \r\n<li>200x180 X 70 x 40\r\n<li>Digital \r\n</ol>\r\n', 'images/products/Dental/Oral-Pathology/861999.png', '', '2014-07-18 14:01:45'),
